/* =====================================================================
 * Combat Robot v2 — tabbed mobile-friendly config UI.
 *
 * Tabs (URL hash changes the active tab):
 *   #controller  pairing + live gamepad
 *   #outputs     per-output card editor (direction, source, deadzone)
 *   #settings    WiFi, board rev, OTA
 *   #about       status + links
 *
 * Endpoints used:
 *   GET  /api/status          — board state (also polled for tabs that aren't outputs)
 *   GET  /api/config          — saved output config, polled once on load
 *   GET  /api/config/sources  — input-source list, polled once on load
 *   POST /api/config          — save output config (body = JSON patch)
 *   POST /api/pair/start      — enter pairing mode
 *   POST /api/pair/cancel     — leave pairing mode
 *   POST /api/pair/clear      — clear whitelist
 *   POST /api/board/rev?rev=N — set board rev override
 *   POST /api/board/reset     — clear board rev override
 *   POST /api/ota             — multipart firmware upload
 *   WS   /ws                  — real-time controller state when connected
 * ===================================================================== */

